verbose_text: Since the effects of Nino 1 + 2 have been removed when defining the CP El Nino (Kao & Yu, 2009; Yu & Tae Kim, 2010), we find the MAM CP El Nino is associated a reversed dipole pattern of ozone, with decreased surface JJA ozone in the middle and southern Atlantic states and increased ozone in the south central states.
